  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6c542dad-6316-4122-bc89-a56f1fc38bf9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8C958976-9F25-4B08-8558-E8BB5FEA8FF5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D2D7EC96-5953-4405-9AE2-6386A7C3E23A\">안녕하세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-DD23CB29-98F1-45DB-9B3D-8C4F3515F7D5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D875B72F-3F49-4A83-A86C-C540B926C8F4\">이수한의원 문학진 원장입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-E299B9B0-B27B-4686-9AA6-9C315FD52C4A\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5FFF991E-19C7-4D0C-B51F-1506E7E1481F\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4F6BB5CA-2531-4434-A3EE-571BA84AC0B4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-097564A0-9FCC-47AB-9641-61F927BAC9E7\">스트레스는 만병의 근원이라고 하죠. 그만큼 스트레스는 우리 건강에 위협적이라는 뜻입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-205A218D-9BA6-4719-9D8E-8A7645753847\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-74817B4B-6D17-42EF-9F87-CB63F99CB298\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2EDB07F6-3DA2-43DA-904D-43ED063D0E67\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3443554C-A846-48B4-9970-687272B51539\">스트레스를 받으면 우리 몸에 뭔가 좋지 않은 변화가 생기는걸 어렴풋이 느낄 수 있습니다. (감각이 좋은 분 또는 스트레스에 대한 신체 변화를 자주 겪어본 분들은 &#x27;명확히&#x27; 느끼기도 합니다)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9511D9D7-A50B-4489-AA13-C40C713BCF03\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-E626B672-7666-4C04-98D7-2535E042BF38\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-16A68528-BA39-4E97-BB05-9DD92AF62FD7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-59E218FC-BC50-4AF5-999B-F07DAE05B857\">스트레스는 도대체 어떻게 우리 몸에 여러가지 변화를 만들어 낼까?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-B7D41BA8-A80D-47AA-9673-44AA657E2141\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-E4F06B97-D1C7-4EB6-A965-5C913E2A719B\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-DB2411BE-72F0-4FE6-9B5B-D67181C0D86A\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D9072B3D-0E46-4AEF-B486-8509EDFAE24C\"><a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222850980468\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222850980468</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-large_image\" id=\"SE-280f2ba1-d81e-4171-9d29-911216ed3c8f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-large_image se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-oglink\">\n                                <a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222850980468\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <img src=\"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src